{"tid":988963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"上 海 開 騷 幾 乎 仆 街 譚 伯 逃 過 一 劫","createTime":"2019-01-20T13:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T15:14:38.000Z","uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"31ab9e6ea286622304b07574ab64ad38d2acdc77","tid":988963,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gj535rF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgj535rF.png&h=77e0201b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民就拍到阿倫幾乎跌落窿嘅短片，片中見到阿倫唱完「若最終只有離開」呢句後，由於要配合歌曲段落停頓關係，舞台燈光效果調校暗咗，喺呢個時候，點知舞台機關提早打開，台上出現一個窿，阿倫踏後一步時失平衡，成個人側埋一邊幾乎跌落窿，嚇到身旁嘅女舞蹈員急忙伸手去扶，好在阿倫身手敏捷，一個轉身彈跳幾步終於企番穩，女舞蹈員即刻拖實阿倫，驚魂甫定嘅阿倫望住台上嘅窿手指指，自己都忍唔住笑出嚟，之後行番台中間繼續唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n網民睇完片都替阿倫抹一把汗，留言：「天啊，真是太令人心有餘悸了。幸虧校長身手敏捷，否則台下眾多的歌迷情人們都會心碎的。」、「話晒做過黃飛鴻，身手唔係流噶~不過真的要小心再小心啊，當時嚇死了！」"},{"pid":"c84879cc61636c45aa675ec4aad030c4db3951e3","tid":988963,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f517246579a80cc316aa00928a75f76fee3687","tid":988963,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba9bcbfa6971ff0cca696eb47fc070dd67a274c","tid":988963,"uid":135169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"仆街譚伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc11a18c6358a5ee55662f8416343b66913d38a","tid":988963,"uid":1790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"咁都死唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91b1720ff380e06f0d61b4c63c662334a9d21a8","tid":988963,"uid":9394,"li